/* Llama2 Fixed - Bare-Metal UEFI Inference Kernel
 * Combines: minimal structure + ARM Optimized math + correct tokenizer
 * Based on Andrej Karpathy's llama2.c (MIT License)
 * Fixed by: Analysis December 2025
