**Type System**
- Primitive types: `u8, u16, u32, u64, i8..i64, f16, f32, f64, bf16`
- Tensor type: `Tensor[dtype, dim0, dim1?, ...]` — shape-checked at compile time
- Pointer types: `*T` (raw), `&T` (borrowed ref), `owned T` (moved), `ref T` (borrowed)
- Optional: `?T` — no null pointers, explicit optionality
- Result: `!T` — no exceptions, explicit error propagation

